me? The toy featured in this video is the
Barbie Kelly Playground Playset. Which was

originally released in 1998. This set comes
with an adorable tree house. With a big pink

slide where the kids can slide down to the

Kelly swing. It also comes with a pink sandbox
with a sand pile, shovel and ball. Plus the

Kelly dolls can play on a duck themed Teeter-Toter.
For more fun the kids can play on Merry-Go-Round.

You can spin it from up top or you can spin
it from the bottom. It has a giraffe an elephant

or a turtle to ride on. And last but not least
is the the Kelly train. It's go the train

engine where the Kelly doll can stand up or
two train cars for two more Kelly dolls. If

you liked this video please click like and
Subscribe with the little Cookie Monster above

me. And in the comments tell me what flavor

a picture to watch another fun toy video.
Thank's for watching and have a great day!
